    <ul>
        <li>Pure SVG rendering - no Canvas or WebGL required</li>
        <li>CSS-based animations with smooth transitions</li>
        <li>Responsive sizing with viewBox</li>
        <li>Dark mode support via CSS variables</li>
        <li>Accessibility with ARIA labels</li>
